head.title: Paid Notice: Deaths BARNES, HENRIETTA JOSEPHINE

hedline.hl1: Paid Notice: Deaths BARNES, HENRIETTA JOSEPHINE

block.p: BARNES - Henrietta Josephine. Died October 26, 2000. at NYU Medical Center at age 90. Born August 28, 1910 in Des Moines, Iowa. Grew up in Fullerton, Nebraska. Survived by cousins and a host of loving friends throughout the U.S. No service planned. Statements of remembrance may be sent to Victoria Haas, 306 South 3rd Ave., Maywood, IL 60153 or Nina Shelden, 1709 134th Ave, South East, #
